  "reference_number": "RUS1992",
  "remarks": "\nYury Anatolyevich\n CHIKHANCHIN is an involved person under the Russia (Sanctions) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019 on the basis of the following ground: CHIKHANCHIN is involved in obtaining a benefit from or supporting the Government of Russia through his position as the head of a federal agency subordinate to the President of the Russian Federation, namely the Federal Service for Financial Monitoring. \n",
